{"tid":126328,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哈利列納：熱刺未來4年內贏英超","createTime":"2017-02-19T09:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T10:25:21.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a92dafa993038f9d3a7aa72168b2507400e6358d","tid":126328,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:12:31.000Z","msg":"前熱刺主帥哈利列納坦言喜歡熱刺刻下的踢法，預期在領隊普捷天奴帶領下，在未來3至4年將成為英超冠軍。<br />\n熱刺雖然自1961年以來，從未染指過英格蘭頂級聯賽冠軍，但他們表現總算穩定，近年在英超名列前茅，而在現任領隊普捷天奴帶領下，上季以第3名完成球季，今季亦同樣暫處於第3位。前熱刺領隊哈利列納（Harry Redknapp）認為，熱刺成為英超冠軍之日並非遙遠。 該名現任約旦國家隊主帥在BBC第5頻道接受訪問時說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">他們在普捷天奴帶領下表現出色，我絕對喜愛他們的踢法和眾後衛的速度，熱刺將會繼續交出好表現，在<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未來</span></span>3到4年勝出英超。</span>」 「也許他們會筋疲力盡，也許他（普捷天奴）沒有作出輪換，他大可添加多3到4名頂級球員，讓陣容更具深度。」列納補充。<br />\n<br />\n未來隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef59b8aa8243b58a3bb2673c49b891904f01fce","tid":126328,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1edd513922b30bf0a20d3c0a81bd426ce1edd66","tid":126328,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:40:15.000Z","msg":"我哋有未來<br />\n你哋車狗有咩?<br />\n世三?"},{"pid":"04089dc477d01f94700eacda7af00f08714d08b9","tid":126328,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:41:20.000Z","msg":"留明待笑"},{"pid":"c8f6c2887d8c387e247439c770dd8e32951a8a1f","tid":126328,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T09:46:54.000Z","msg":"未來熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c33b22d82291b107fa386910f6fd01fd801c38","tid":126328,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T10:25: